data.description: Get in while you can, to tour this lovely home located on the outside of the Neosho city limits and on over an acre of land. With 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, an office space, 2 living areas, and just over 2k sq.ft., you have the perfect recipe for comfortable living. Throw in the detached, two car garage and life doesn't get any better!
